{
    "name": "Streamer",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Streamers present content live via digital platforms, attracting avid audiences that love these celebrities\u2019 skill, conversation, idiosyncrasies, and knowledge. Streamed content might encompass anything from cooking hacks to gladiatorial home- and-garden tips for growing giant carnivorous plants like a pro. Streamers who provide content in public places sometimes catch unique footage of crimes or major events, becoming spontaneous journalists or invaluable witnesses. While these serendipitous recordings can earn a streamer fame, chronicling illicit activity can also create dangerous enemies."
        },
        {
            "name": "Celebrities",
            "type": "section",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Interstellar Species",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Interstellar Species pg. 156",
                        "alt": "Interstellar Species pg. 156",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq02d4w?Starfinder-Interstellar-Species"
                    },
                    "page": 156
                }
            ],
            "html": "Celebrities shine in ways that often draw admiration, adoration, or amusement from fans across their home worlds and beyond. They regularly engage with fans through interviews, social media, and special appearances, boosting their sway in the court of public opinion. Some celebrities use their massive platforms to influence policy and elections, and it\u2019s not uncommon for groups with specific political or corporate interests to secretly plant or sponsor celebrities to advance particular agendas."
        }
    ],
